<li>McDonough, James L., "Battle of Shiloh", <i><a href="http://books.google.com/books?id=SdrYv7S60fgC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0#PPP1,M1" class="external text" title="http://books.google.com/books?id=SdrYv7S60fgC&amp;printsec=frontcover&amp;source=gbs_summary_r&amp;cad=0#PPP1,M1" rel="nofollow">Encyclopedia of the American Civil War: A Political, Social, and Military History</a></i>, Heidler, David S., and Heidler, Jeanne T., eds., W. W. Norton &amp; Company, 2000, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/039304758X" class="internal">ISBN 0-393-04758-X</a>.</li>
